To run the program, open the folder in terminal and run the following instructions:

g++ assembler.cpp
./a.out

The following files are generated:

optable.txt : contains the optable
symtable.txt : contains the symtable
object.txt : equivalent object code generated
source.txt: for verifying that source code (sample_input.txt) is correctly converted
intermediate.txt: code generated after the first pass of the assembler
